{
  "page": "House Serrett",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Serrett of Silverhill</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Serrett.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Serrett.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b2/House_Serrett.svg/250px-House_Serrett.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b2/House_Serrett.svg/375px-House_Serrett.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b2/House_Serrett.svg/500px-House_Serrett.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"width:100%;min-width:300px;position:relative;z-index:100;border:0 grey solid;margin-top:-3em;margin-bottom:1em;\"><div style=\"display: table; width: calc(100% - 80px); height: 28px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px; margin: 0px auto 0px; padding: 0;border:0; position: relative; border-collapse:collapse; text-align: center; font-family: &#39;Uncial Antiqua&#39;; color: #00579c; background: #bb8;\">\n  <div style=\"display:table-cell; vertical-align: middle; padding: 4px; clip-path: polygon(2px 2px, calc(100% - 2px) 2px, calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), 2px calc(100% - 2px)); background: #ede7a9;\">I Have No Rival</div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -3; left: -42px; clip-path: polygon(calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), 5px calc(100% - 2px), calc(25% + 3px) 50%, 5px 2px, calc(100% - 2px) 2px, 75% 50%, calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), calc(100% - 2px) 5px, calc(75% + 3px) 50%); background: #ede7a9;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -4; left: -42px; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%, 25% 50%); background: #bb8;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -3; right: -42px; clip-path: polygon(2px calc(100% - 2px), calc(100% - 5px) calc(100% - 2px), calc(75% - 3px) 50%, calc(100% - 5px) 2px, 2px 2px, 25% 50%, 2px calc(100% - 2px), 2px 5px, calc(25% - 3px) 50%); background: #ede7a9;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -4; right: -42px; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 75% 50%, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); background: #bb8;\"></div></div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nA peacock in his pride on cream<br />(<i>Carnation, a peacock in his pride proper</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Seat</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Silverhill\" title=\"Silverhill\">Silverhill</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nLord  <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Serrett\" title=\"Lord Serrett\">Serrett</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Founded</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal_Invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal Invasion\">Andal Invasion</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Serrett of Silverhill</b> is a noble house from <a href=\"/index.php/Silverhill\" title=\"Silverhill\">Silverhill</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a>. It is one of the principal houses sworn to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>They blazon their arms with a <a href=\"/index.php/Peacock\" title=\"Peacock\">peacock</a> in his pride on cream.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Their words according to semi-canon sources are \"I Have No Rival\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#House_Serrett_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Serrett at the end of the third century</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Serrett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>House Serrett was formed by the union of <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andal</a> nobles during the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The mother of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harras_Harlaw\" title=\"Harras Harlaw\">Harras Harlaw</a> was a Serrett.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Serrett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Serrett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> sees <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Serrett\" title=\"Lord Serrett\">Lord Serrett</a> and his retainers in the center of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> army at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_on_the_Green_Fork\" title=\"Battle on the Green Fork\">battle on the Green Fork</a>, riding alongside Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a>. When Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> named his son Tyrion as Acting <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, Tyrion mentions Lord Serrett as an alternative over himself.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Serrett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The colors of House Serrett are seen by <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> leaving <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> with Tywin's army.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Serrett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The Serrett peacock is worn by the serjeant at the gates of <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a> encountered by <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Serrett_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Serrett at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Serrett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Serrett at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Serretts during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Serrett\" title=\"Lord Serrett\">Lord Serrett</a>, present at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_on_the_Green_Fork\" title=\"Battle on the Green Fork\">battle on the Green Fork</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The mother of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harras_Harlaw\" title=\"Harras Harlaw\">Harras Harlaw</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Serrett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Westerlands.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Appendix\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"refe